Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:02.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆前情提要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Previously on "Salem"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,私通者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fornicator!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他在寻找\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He searches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么女巫在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So where is the witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:13.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果不能阻止他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If he cannot be stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:19.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那就变成一个全新的游戏了 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}well, then it's an entirely new game, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:24.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你父亲做的每一件事 都是为了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything your father does, he does for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:29.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不想再当你的顾客了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I no longer want to be your customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:32.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真爱不能买卖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}True love cannot be bought or sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:34.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们把梦变成现实吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's just live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还爱着约翰 奥尔登\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You still love John Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:40.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那场盛大的仪式恰恰是在累觉不爱的心里腐败发酵的最好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The grand rite ferments best in a loveless heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:42.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他听从于我的指令\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He serves at my behest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不会因为你跑出来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He won't come out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:51.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的因克里斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My dear Increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:54.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们能够在镇上看到您多久呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How long may we enjoy your presence in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:57.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一直到塞勒姆镇最后一个卖身魔鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Until every last Devil's whore of a witch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,的女巫死光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in Salem is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,堕落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Depravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:07.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还能找到一个更恰当的词汇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can there be a more apt word
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:09.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来描述现阶段你们这个公平的城市吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to describe the current state of your fair city?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,酗酒 变态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Drink, perversity,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:13.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恶习 人们相互展示和感受到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}abominations of each and every variety
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:15.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,全都是这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}offered and received.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且就在我们祀奉内心的魔鬼时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And even as we cater to our inner demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:21.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们还让真正的恶魔肆无忌惮起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we have allowed actual demons to flourish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些巫师们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他不应该出现在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He was not supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:26.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他应该在没有上帝保佑的航船上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Living vessels of godlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么为什么他在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So why is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,伊甸园的蛇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The serpent from eden...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他要来看看他的儿子取得了什么成就\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He came to see what his son had accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们都听说过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have listened and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:33.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那他为什么待着不走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And why is he staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为他看到了他那儿子都干了些什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He saw what his son had accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:39.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们之中隐藏着巫师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are witches hidden amongst us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而在塞勒姆的你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and you people of Salem,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:45.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被饮酒和淫乱引诱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}seduced by drink and by flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一步步沉迷不醒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}are happily blinded to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:48.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在此\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Standing before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在青天白日之下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with the certainty of the rising sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:55.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,向你们保证 这一切将会改变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I assure you this will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:02.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,牧师 您的话语非常鼓舞人心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Reverend, your words are inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,您回来是英格兰的损失 是我们的好运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}England's loss is our gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:07.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我相信你丈夫的情况一定是越来越好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I trust your husband's condition is improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不幸的是并没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sadly, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那就帮我告诉乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, please tell George
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不久就会再去看他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I shall visit him again at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:16.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我的探望能够让他感觉好一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Perhaps my presence may be of some comfort to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 那是肯定的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, how could it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,妙不可言啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have no words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像是对于看到了上帝面容的人来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Like a man who's seen the face of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只有因敬畏而无声才是最好的表达方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Only an awed silence is the appropriate response.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你这样一说 真是毁情绪啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And like that, the mood is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 你 你父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, your... your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:58.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他正 他在人群中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's... he's in the common.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,前呼后拥 当然了 把他说的每一个字都奉若真理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With a crowd, no doubt, hanging on his every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他是 被前呼后拥 但是他没说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With a crowd, yes, but he's not speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你还是让他跟别人困扰去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, then you must have him confused with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:10.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他正朝这边过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's walking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说的朝这边 意思是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And by "This way," You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不能让他看到我在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He cannot find me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而要开始清洗我们的塞勒姆镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And where better to begin our cleansing of Salem
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哪能比这肮脏至极的淫窟更合适呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}than in its most vile den?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,后边楼梯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The back stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不对 你 那你得穿过平台\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no, no, no, y-you'll cross the landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,格洛丽安娜 我父亲不会理解我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gloriana, my father does not understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他从来都不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He never has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-如果让他发现我 -快藏在床底下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- If he discovers me... - Gloriana: Under the bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:40.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-什么 快藏在床底下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?! - Gloriana: Under the bed now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的圣经呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's my Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我 我 我没看见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I-I-I don't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,麦哲牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Reverend Mather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你认识我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:08.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,整个省里面谁不认识您呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is there anyone in the province who doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你一个人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:21.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我与我的上帝同在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm here with my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:27.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有他的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His words, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:32.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在最危险的时候 那些话给了我极大的安慰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They offer great comfort in these perilous times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即使是对像我这样的女人来讲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Even for a woman like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们感觉不到吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you not sense it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:55.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,罪孽和巫术混杂在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The commingling of sin and sorcery?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你甚至可以尝到它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can almost taste it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,撒旦的毒酒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Satan's toxic nectar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:10.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为了转移你们的注意 平息你们的怒火\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}designed to divert and disarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:28.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这温柔乡的女主人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The proprietress of this charming establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今天要什么样的啊 牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What'll it be today, Reverend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,纤瘦柔软的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thin and pliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还是丰满调皮的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or thick and playful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,跟长辈说话要小心 女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mind your betters, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:48.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我做的是清白生意 你什么都抓不到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I run an honest house. You'll find nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就是以我之名立誓 要在你这什么都抓不到的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have made my name finding things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:54.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抓到点东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}where there is nothing to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,鸢尾根\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Orris root?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:12.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,陌生人每天进进出出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Strangers tramp in and out of here every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不能确定他们都有什么目的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I do not know what substances they carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:38.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,铸造石\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Casting stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:01.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆的治安官啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Selectmen of Salem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:04.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们发现了一个女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We've uncovered a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:55.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们之中有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}One of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在我们最惶恐的时候弃船了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Exactly what we feared the minute he stepped off that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在 你们知道这意味着什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now, well, you know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就算我没跟你一起恐慌\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just because I don't share your panic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也不代表我没发现问题所在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}doesn't mean I don't grasp the stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会向她逼问我们的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He will press her for names,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得她最先会供出谁呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and whose will be she tempted to provide?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她太大意了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was careless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,竟然把能泄露身份的东西留在身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}leaving objects of her craft so close at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就因为她的失误 我们都将会被烧死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And for that carelessness, we may all burn,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,更别提还想举行什么盛大的仪式了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to say nothing of what will become of our grand rite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在这歇斯底里也无济于事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your hysteria offers no solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:21.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,马布只是需要一个小小的提醒 什么才是我们想要她做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mab simply needs to be reminded what is expected of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:22.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的缄默\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是对的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我马上就去看她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I shall pay her a visit at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他让人生畏 老麦哲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He is formidable, the senior Mather,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:38.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一边恐吓一边狩猎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}part bully, part bloodhound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,马布自始至终都忠于我们巫群\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mab has been loyal to the hive throughout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我担心的不是马布\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is not Mab that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:47.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因克里斯说要再来拜访\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Increase promises to pay another visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得还需要多久他才发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How long before he realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:51.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治不是生病了而是被下蛊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that George is not sick, but spelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,又是被谁下的毒手 是我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And at whose hands? Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那就阻止他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then prevent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因克里斯是想他方便的时候才来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Increase may visit at his pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:04.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而什么原因能让挚爱的妻子在卧病在床的丈夫最需要照看的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for what loving wife would leave her ailing husband at home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,将其独自留在家中呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when his condition demands attention at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今天这么早就喝酒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're drinking early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你了解我父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you knew my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你了解我的父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you knew my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就会为我能等如此之久而称赞我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you'd commend me for waiting this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 你把你父亲说得像是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, the way you speak of him, you make him sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有人性\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Inhuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-对 -好样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}-Yes. -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看来我对他的描述丝毫不差\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then I have painted an accurate picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:41.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不信吗 你自己瞧瞧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't believe me? See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿 我一整个早上都在找你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton, I've been in search of you all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我早该料到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I supposed I should have realized
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你泡在酒坛子里了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you would be somewhere where whiskey is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,老爸 这是约翰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father, this is John...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,约翰 奥尔登\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}John Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:58.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你父亲和我是大学同学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your father and I were classmates at university.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到你 上尉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}An honor, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真的 我对你无比尊敬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Truly, I can have no greater respect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为你在战场上舍生忘死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}than for a man who has risked his life in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:12.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可悲了 现在不是所有的年轻人都有你这样的勇气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sadly, not all young men possess the same mettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么风把你吹来了 父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What brings you, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:17.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我十分惊奇地发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I am shocked to discover
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆竟然自甘堕落伤风败俗到这种程度\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the extent of the depravity and immorality in Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:25.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,人们需要有人来提醒他们犯下罪孽后的代价\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The people need a reminder of the wages of their sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是不报 时候未到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And so they will get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-哼 -在周日的布道上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}-Mm-hmm. -In Sunday's sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:36.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们需要听到你的声音 就是此刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They need to hear your voice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给平民的公众朗诵\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A public recitation on the commons,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,用蒙上罪孽的脸来阐述\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}illustrated by the face of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,蒙上罪孽的脸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The face of sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And Cotton?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的圣经\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:28.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,波士顿的医院在等他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The hospital in Boston awaits him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它是我寻到治愈方法的唯一希望了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is my only hope to find a cure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他的情况日趋严重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for his worsening condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:42.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以撒 你对我丈夫的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And, Isaac, your feelings towards my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,针对他曾经做过的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for what he once did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是可以理解的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're understandable,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是你在他最需要的时候帮助他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but to help him in his hour of need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为我展示了你的真正度量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}shows me the true measure of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我为此对你永怀感激\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For which I am forever grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们在黎明时会到波士顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We will be in Boston by daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能见一下被告吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A moment with the accused?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的 地方官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是来杀我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've come here to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:44.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是我的分内之事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It would be within my right to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,家有家法 国有国规\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The code of the hive is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 不 我们同意饶恕你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But, no, we have agreed to spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我决不允许发生第二次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I would allow nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:55.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 在目前这个问题上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still... to the issue at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会审问你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He will interrogate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会守口如瓶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I will give him nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:04.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到死我都不会出卖女巫的事业\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will swallow the blackened pill before I betray the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:06.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你的目的 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That will be your intent, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,直到他拷问你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}until he tortures you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后 听到你痛苦的嘶喊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then, hearing your cries of pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会更加残忍地拷问你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}tortures you some more,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,此时你就会哀求他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}at which point you will beg for him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让你说出一个名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to allow you to offer a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,甚至只是为了暂时逃离肉体的痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}even if only to release yourself from the agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当这一切发生的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它会发生的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And it will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:31.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只能分散你的注意力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have just the distraction for you to provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲 你晚上去哪里了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where do you go at night, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:48.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安妮 还没睡呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Anne. Awake at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,母亲说我不应该问这种问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mother says I shouldn't ask such questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我仅仅需要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that I should simply be grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对你为了我们所做出的牺牲表示感激\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for the sacrifices you make on our behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:59.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,胡说 随便问\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nonsense. Ask whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:04.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今晚我在专心处理这个镇上的事务\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tonight I was preoccupied with business of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你相信她是个女巫吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And do you believe she is a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:18.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在监狱里找到的那个女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The woman you sought out at the jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你跟踪我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You followed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道那些所谓的牺牲究竟是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I simply wanted to know what those sacrifices were
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:25.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么它们总是见不得阳光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and why they seem to be so often made in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,起先你私窥我的房间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}First you snoop about in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:32.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,翻看我的东西 而现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}unearthing my belongings, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:44.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我不相信她是女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I do not believe she is a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她只是个可爱又可怜的女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She is but a sad, lonely woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴听到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am glad to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆的人还有些常识\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}there is some common sense left in Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,晚安 父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good night, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,晚安 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good night, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,求你 我是无辜的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please! I am innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:20.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为你使用巫术的罪孽进行辩护\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have pled guilty to the practice of witchcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是这种辩护并不足以使你脱罪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But such a plea is not sufficient to spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我需要的是名单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want names of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know of no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我发誓我是无辜的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No! I swear I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他疯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在如此美好的一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要说出一个你的同伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Only the name of a fellow witch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就会被赦免\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}will spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有同伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know of no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我再问一遍 先警告你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will ask again, but first a caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,下一次 海水可不仅仅只填满你的嘴巴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The next time, the saltwater that filled your mouth only
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的喉咙 你的肺都会充斥了海水\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}will travel down your throat into your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后你挣扎着要辨别的滋味\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And then the taste you struggle to discern
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:25.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是海水味 不是空气 而是死亡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}will not be of water, nor of air, but of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:39.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只等你说出一个同伙的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I wait only for the name of a fellow witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I will give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是她 格洛丽安娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her! Gloriana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:59.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不可能 不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:01.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这肯定是弄错了 不可能的 父亲 这肯定弄错了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is a mistake. No, father, this is a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,昂布里小姐不是女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Miss embry is no witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你来这儿只是旁观 不应插手此事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are here to observe, not to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听我说 父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen to me, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这正是我设法要告诉你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is what I have tried to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在我目睹了它是对的 就是我们都错了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and now I see it to be true... That we have been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:11.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们一腔热血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That in our zeal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想要驱逐撒旦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to rid Satan from our midst,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,却变成了屠戮无辜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we are instead killing innocents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要对我说教\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do not presume to instruct me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们是在助纣为虐啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are doing the Devil's work for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以我倾其一生的事业是个错误\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And my life's work is a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:28.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,尊敬地说 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Respectfully... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,靠边站\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stand aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,求你 父亲 求求你 放了她吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please, father, I beg you... spare her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,滚开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请听我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我听着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不会再让你扮演傻瓜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I will no longer let you act the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你确定我就是那个傻瓜吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are sure it is I who acts the fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把她关进笼子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Take her to the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:59.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿 柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton. Cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:06.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿 柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton! Cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 怎么了 西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, Lord. What is it, Mr. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,努力呼吸一下 西布利先生 就是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Try to breathe, Mr. Sibley. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢呼吸 西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Slow breath, Mr. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是这样 很好很简单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's it, nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲 你没有任何证据\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father, you have no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,胡说 我有那个被公认为的女巫的供词\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nonsense. I have the word of an admitted witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是那个耍魔鬼巫术的女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A woman who practices the Devil's craft?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你竟然相信她去指认其他人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You trust her to finger others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:05.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是不是所有的控告都让你肾上腺素飙升\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do all accusations stir such passions in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:08.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或者那个妓女的案子有什么特别之处吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or is there something unique about the whore's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:13.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道这些人 我生活在他们中间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know these people. I have lived among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布里小姐不是撒旦的工具\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Miss embry is no tool of Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:21.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那如果她做魔鬼烙印的测试呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And if she were to be examined for the Devil's marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,测试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}An examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我有这个自信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:30.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我确信 你们什么都找不到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I am certain... That you would find nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:33.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,事实上 是的 我支持你去做这件事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In fact, yes, I would encourage you to settle the issue
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即刻执行测试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and conduct the exam at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:38.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Me? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是 我把这事儿交给你去办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I will leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:48.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你去测试被告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You will examine the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这不是我要的反应\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That wasn't the reaction I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也不是我要的问候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nor the greeting I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那天晚上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The other night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们说过的 做过的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What we said... what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么 你后悔了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What, do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:30.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我唯一的遗憾就是我们再也不能那样了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My only regret is that it can never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我已经结婚了 约翰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm a married woman, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和一个疾病缠身的男人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With a very sick husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:39.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利先生再也不能顺我心的死去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Sibley would never do me the favor of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都知道这点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We both know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他被送去医院了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He was taken to hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他肯定会回来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}From where he will surely return...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:48.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一如既往的活着 享受婚姻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}As alive and married as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:51.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是这个原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is that the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:52.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有其他了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nothing else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是因为恐惧吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not a fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:22:00.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或者某个你觉得我接受不了的秘密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or a secret that you think I couldn't accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为塞勒姆从来没有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because there is no one in Salem
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:03.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能够卸下沉重的过往\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}unburdened by their past...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:07.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也不能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:10.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 西布利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:17.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hope you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:35.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲 求求你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:37.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有印记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:57.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把她翻过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Turn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:12.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:14.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把她衣服撩起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Raise her smock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:27.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,依然什么都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:30.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上半身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The upper torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:40.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上半身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The upper torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.58,0:24:37.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以你看 就像我保证的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, you see, as I assured you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.69,0:24:39.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他身上没有恶魔使者的标志\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}she bears no signs of a Devil's agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.52,0:24:41.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有疤痕 没有女巫乳头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}no blemishes, no witches' teats.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:44.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这些我都会在她的审判上提及\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All of which I will be sure to mention at her trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.06,0:24:45.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她还要审判\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:48.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我已经向你证明了她身上没有标记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I have proven to you she is without marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:52.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你忘了嘛 我们不是法官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Have you forgotten? We are not judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:55.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们只是寻找真相\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are simply seekers of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.10,0:24:58.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,审判权在行政委员手上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The power of verdict rests with the selectmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.54,0:25:01.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这里是塞勒姆 你知道他们会怎样投票\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is Salem. You know how they will vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.04,0:25:03.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你正好把你的愤怒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, then you save
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:05.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的放肆无礼向他们发泄吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your rage and your impudence for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.87,0:25:26.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧 今天又有个女人被指控为女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Another woman was accused today... as you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.87,0:25:29.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这场女巫恐慌简直要把人逼疯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's madness, this witch panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.71,0:25:31.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 真令人惋惜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, it is regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.94,0:25:34.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,惋惜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Regrettable?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.08,0:25:35.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想要我干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What would you have me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:37.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你可以站出来反驳他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You could speak out, rail against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.78,0:25:41.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有一堆选择 可你却什么都不做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have any number of options beyond nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.12,0:25:43.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我孤掌难鸣啊 也许你对我期望值太高了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am one man. Perhaps you expect too much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:45.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许你为这做的太少了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Perhaps you are content with too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.32,0:25:48.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,注意你的言辞 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hold your tongue, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.22,0:25:50.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就是不理解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.36,0:25:53.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么他如此乐意看到人们被绞死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}why he's so content to see people hang...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.73,0:25:55.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好像他内心对此暗暗欢喜似的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Almost as if he secretly likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.66,0:25:58.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢你含沙射影\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't appreciate the insinuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.33,0:26:00.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我哪里含沙射影了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What insinuation is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.90,0:26:02.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是想说我是那种\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That I was somehow in league
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.44,0:26:03.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,内心尖刻的清教徒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with the murdering puritans.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.74,0:26:06.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 不 我根本不是这个意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, no, that was not my insinuation at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.81,0:26:09.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,事实上 恰恰相反\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In fact, it was quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.55,0:26:13.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你是什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And what might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.62,0:26:17.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是这样 我 我突然感觉很累\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, I'm... I'm suddenly very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.59,0:26:18.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你到底在指责我什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you accusing me of?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.92,0:26:20.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想我该去躺一会儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think I should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.52,0:26:23.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安妮 你解释清楚前哪都不准去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Anne, do not walk away until you have explained yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.36,0:26:25.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,安妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Anne!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.81,0:26:40.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能问你个问题嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}May I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.21,0:26:42.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他为什么讨厌你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why does he hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.44,0:26:44.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,原因只有两个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Two reasons only...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.35,0:26:46.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一是我的所作所为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For what I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.48,0:26:50.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,二是我的无所作为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And what I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.15,0:26:52.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么你已经向他表明了 你站在那姑娘那边了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And you've appealed to him on the girl's behalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.25,0:26:55.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再说一遍 他根本不鸟我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Repeatedly. He does not regard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.86,0:27:00.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说实话 他不鸟任何人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Truth told, he does not regard anyone except...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.53,0:27:02.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,除了你 约翰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.73,0:27:04.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿 这不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.13,0:27:07.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他希望我成为像你一样的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are everything he ever wished me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.50,0:27:09.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是战争英雄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are a hero in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.81,0:27:14.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,坚毅刚强\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are a man without weakness or frailty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.38,0:27:17.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿 无意冒犯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.35,0:27:21.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去乞求一个混蛋清教徒正确行事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Begging another puritan asshole to do the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.95,0:27:25.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,成功过么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Since when has it worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.05,0:27:28.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-现在又怎么会成功 -你说得没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- And why would it work now? - You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.46,0:27:32.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,任何人都不该被迫在我父亲面前低声下气 卑躬屈膝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No man should be forced to humble himself before my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.33,0:27:36.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我到塞勒姆已经好几个月了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have been in Salem for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.67,0:27:40.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有很多朋友也有不少敌人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have made allies and enemies in scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:43.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我最亲近的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But the closest thing that I have come to a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.27,0:27:48.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:50.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.91,0:27:54.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我乞求你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.62,0:27:56.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去找我父亲说情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To appeal to my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.85,0:28:00.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你稍微有一点看得起我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if there is some small part of you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:02.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也能称我一声朋友的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that can call me a friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.81,0:28:18.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.00,0:28:46.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Sibley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.04,0:28:56.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Sibley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.36,0:29:10.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.36,0:29:12.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,救命 以撒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Help me, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.63,0:29:18.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你能说话了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.03,0:29:21.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,神奇的上帝重赋我言语之能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Lord's miraculous workings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:23.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在流血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're leaking blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.21,0:29:26.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以救救我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Which is why I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.57,0:29:29.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快去塞勒姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go to Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.21,0:29:34.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给我带医生和药品来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Return with supplies and one to administer them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.48,0:29:36.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要我帮你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.85,0:29:39.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.82,0:29:44.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还记得你烙印我的那一天嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you remember the day you marked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.63,0:29:51.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在我身上烙下私通者的印记的那天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The day you seared my flesh with the sign of the fornicator?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:54.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还记得吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.00,0:29:58.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想这之后你没有一刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I would imagine that not a moment has since passed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.71,0:30:00.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不希望我死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that you didn't wish me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.38,0:30:06.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在机会来了 你甚至不用动一根手指头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And now your chance, without even raising a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.75,0:30:10.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要你走开 我就必死无疑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Walk away, and I will surely die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.19,0:30:15.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我为什么不呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.16,0:30:19.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为在你期待复仇的同时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because while you desired revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.36,0:30:24.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我真心为这样对你而感到后悔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I bore regret for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.10,0:30:27.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说得好听\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Words.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.54,0:30:30.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你帮帮我 我会给予你更多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then help me, and I will shower you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.31,0:30:33.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不光是美言 更有黄金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}not with words, but gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.31,0:30:37.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,比你期望的还要多的黄金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}more than you've ever hoped to possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.08,0:30:40.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,黄金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.45,0:30:43.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要把药和 和西布利夫人带来就行了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To return with... with medicines and Mrs. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.72,0:30:45.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.02,0:30:45.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.95,0:30:48.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是因克瑞斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.26,0:30:49.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因克瑞斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Increase?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.72,0:30:51.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别跟我妻子说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell my wife nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.66,0:30:55.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快去把因克瑞斯 马瑟带来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bring me Increase Mather at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.83,0:30:59.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快去 小子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go now, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.93,0:31:02.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.57,0:31:04.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.27,0:31:06.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.99,0:31:39.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:44.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.57,0:31:47.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.27,0:31:49.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还什么都没说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.24,0:31:52.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是来为那个妓女求情的对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're here to beg for the whore's life, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.07,0:31:55.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我那糊涂儿子叫你来的对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dispatched by my besotted son, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.68,0:31:57.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:01.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那我就开门见山的说了 奥尔登队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, let me save you the trouble, Captain Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:04.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是一定会接受审判的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The decision has been made to take her to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.42,0:32:09.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但请放心 我一定会告诉柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But rest assured I will be sure to tell Cotton
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.09,0:32:11.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你真心诚意的为她求过情了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that your pleas were most heartfelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.39,0:32:15.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,先生 格罗丽安娜不是女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sir... Gloriana is no witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.13,0:32:16.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没错 她不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.53,0:32:20.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我想你也知道 她迷惑了我儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I think you will agree she has bewitched my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.37,0:32:27.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 我父亲是十分敬重你的 牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, my father held you in high regard, Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.01,0:32:29.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,奥尔登先生 是个好人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alden sr. Was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.48,0:32:32.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他的世界观与众不同\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He viewed the world with uncommon reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.45,0:32:36.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没错 可在育儿方面却也与他人无异\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, well, except when it came to his own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.75,0:32:41.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他希望我研习经文\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He wanted me to study scripture,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.76,0:32:44.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我却选择去森林探险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I chose to explore the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.53,0:32:47.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他希望我去读大学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He wanted me to attend university,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.06,0:32:48.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而我却志愿去参军\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I volunteered for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.76,0:32:52.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他到死都认定我一生的选择都是错的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He went to his grave thinking my life's choices mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.20,0:33:00.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即便如此他也同意你这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And yet he allowed you to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.57,0:33:02.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 因为他懂得就事论事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, that's because he knew the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.98,0:33:04.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就事论事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Between?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.31,0:33:06.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可以不爱他儿子的选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Between loving his son's choices
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.68,0:33:08.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但还是爱他的儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and loving his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.20,0:33:26.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,奥尔登队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Captain Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.57,0:33:28.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以撒 怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.64,0:33:31.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,借一步说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.11,0:33:36.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治西布利能说话了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}George Sibley can speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:37.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像我们一样口齿清晰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}As clearly as you or I.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.71,0:33:39.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他受伤了 却不要见他的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And wounded, he doesn't request his wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.55,0:33:41.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-而是要见 -因克瑞斯 马瑟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- but asks for... -Increase Mather.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.42,0:33:45.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他就像贼一样不可信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I trust him no more than a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.59,0:33:48.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但真要违抗那样位高权重的人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But to disobey a man of his standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.99,0:33:52.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你什么都别做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.86,0:33:56.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.56,0:34:00.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你征求我的意见所以我发表观点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You sought my advice, so I offer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:02.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,任他自生自灭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.64,0:34:04.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 再把他丢在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But to leave him any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.51,0:34:06.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,荒郊野外 他还在流血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}than I have in the woods, bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.51,0:34:08.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.18,0:34:12.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.21,0:34:15.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他罪有应得不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Does he deserve anything less?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.02,0:34:17.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他在你的身体上烙下了印记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The man who marked your flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.82,0:34:19.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把我派上了战场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Drove me to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.89,0:34:23.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还像暴君一般统治着塞勒姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And has ruled over Salem like a power-mad king?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:26.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在 他凭什么乞求怜悯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And now, what, he begs for compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.03,0:34:28.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有合作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cooperation?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.37,0:34:34.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.64,0:34:40.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你爱她 队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know you love her, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.47,0:34:44.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但不管他的死活就是谋杀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But to leave him to die is murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.81,0:34:51.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么都 别干\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:04.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 你要带我去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.47,0:35:09.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你要带我去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me! Where are you taking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.60,0:35:12.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆善良的人们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good people of Salem,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.81,0:35:15.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我已经注意到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it has come to my attention
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:19.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今天这场指控\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that the accusation leveled today
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.65,0:35:22.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是女巫们的一个把戏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}was a trick of the witches...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.72,0:35:28.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个欺骗和混淆视听的邪恶把戏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}An infernal ploy to delude and distract from the truly guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.49,0:35:33.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个女人不是女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This woman is no sorceress.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.96,0:35:38.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因此 她不会被审判\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And therefore she will not go to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.10,0:35:47.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但这个女人自甘堕落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But what her advocates fail to grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.74,0:35:52.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是女巫并不能说明她无罪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is that absence of guilt does not mean innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.88,0:35:58.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以这个妓女绝不是无辜的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For this whore is no innocent... Far from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.42,0:36:01.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她有罪，肉体之罪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She is guilty of sin, sins of the flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.79,0:36:05.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她冒犯上帝 人神共愤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}sins against God, sins both mortal and eternal,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.29,0:36:09.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因此 她不能再涉足塞勒姆半步\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and as such, she warrants no place in Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.50,0:36:10.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.50,0:36:12.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以 我宣判\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And so, by my decree,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.97,0:36:15.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她现被驱逐出此地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}she is hereby banished from our midst,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.94,0:36:20.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即刻生效 不容异议\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}her expulsion immediate and beyond dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.31,0:36:23.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在你 看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And should she... Look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.58,0:36:28.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,永远 不论何种缘由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ever return at any time,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.85,0:36:30.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不得再回到塞勒姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for any reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.65,0:36:34.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你如果再次出现在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you will find yourself once again beside me on the common,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.02,0:36:36.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你肮脏的躯体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your lifeless body dangling
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.12,0:36:39.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,将依旧会被侩子手终结\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}from the wrong end of the hangman's noose.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.39,0:36:40.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,带她走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.23,0:36:41.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.33,0:36:43.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,格洛丽安娜 -柯顿 柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gloriana! - Cotton! Cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.90,0:36:46.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿 柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton! Cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.07,0:36:48.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,格洛丽安娜 -后退 后退\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gloriana! -Stand back. Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.37,0:36:50.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 格洛丽安娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No! Gloriana!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.88,0:36:59.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.05,0:37:07.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,带她走 直到路的尽头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Take her as far as your steeds will travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.39,0:37:13.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并宣告天下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And let it be known
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.09,0:37:16.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,无论是罪恶还是罪人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}neither sin nor sinner
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.26,0:37:20.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在塞勒姆都无立足之地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}have any place in Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.48,0:37:41.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}George.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.75,0:37:44.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道是谁 是怎样做到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know how or by whom,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.49,0:37:47.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但他已经变了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but the familiar has been excised from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.26,0:37:50.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他现在可能正在任何地方告诉任何人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He could be anywhere right now, talking to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:52.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们做的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All that we've worked for,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.63,0:37:55.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我所有的牺牲 瞬间消失殆尽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}all that I've sacrificed, incinerated in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.83,0:37:58.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,冷静下来帮帮我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Calm yourself and help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.79,0:38:19.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,世界之大 皆在变幻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mutare, et notum sumbotis.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.66,0:38:22.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,表象之躯 皆为指引\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Forma enim esse ostendit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.79,0:38:25.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,躯体为本 魂魄为体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Corpus, anima, mens.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.43,0:38:27.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,指引我找到那个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lead me to the one I seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.11,0:38:40.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它会带领我找到他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The creature will lead me to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.64,0:38:44.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,幸运的话 我会尽快找到他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With luck, I will find him quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.01,0:38:46.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有它 我们都可能会被烧死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And without it, we shall all burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.90,0:39:05.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你采用了我的方法啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You take issue with my methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:09.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.51,0:39:14.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要知道 我做的每一件事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What you need to understand is that everything I have done
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:18.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是为了让你能担得起马瑟这个名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}has been to make you worthy of the Mather name.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.18,0:39:22.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我爱她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.25,0:39:24.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要那么说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do not say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.39,0:39:28.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不说话 不代表不爱她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My silence does not make it untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.86,0:39:31.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,若有一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.60,0:39:37.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当你统治这片伟大的土地时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when you are governor of this great land,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.90,0:39:43.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,权利与道德并拥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a man of power and a model of virtue,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.64,0:39:47.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,受到大家敬重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}respected and feared in equal measure,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:50.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你会想到今天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you will trace it back to this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.62,0:39:56.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我将你前进之路的诱惑一一铲除\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The day I removed temptation from your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:22.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-服务员 -有什么需要吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}-You there. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.91,0:40:26.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给我一份红茶 要浓的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bring me some black tea, very strong, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.08,0:40:27.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.49,0:40:34.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不是昨天那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you not the young man
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.39,0:40:37.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把西布利带到波士顿的人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who transported Mr. Sibley to Boston yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.96,0:40:41.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我叫以撒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.07,0:40:42.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-以撒 -嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}-Isaac. -Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.83,0:40:45.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,已经去过波士顿 都回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Boston and back?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.24,0:40:47.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还真快啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Record time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.00,0:40:48.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你真的是个不错的骑士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You must be quite the horseman, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.87,0:40:51.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我可不敢妄称\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I-I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.64,0:40:53.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊 告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.41,0:40:57.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,医生对病人的情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did the physician offer any insight
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.01,0:40:59.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有没有提出什么见解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}into the patient's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.78,0:41:03.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Physician?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.09,0:41:07.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,诊断 或者是 预测\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A diagnosis? Or a prognosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.06,0:41:10.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.13,0:41:12.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我不能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.06,0:41:15.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你确实把西布利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, you did take Mr. Sibley
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.87,0:41:17.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,送到了医院吧 难道不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to the hospital, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.80,0:41:22.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你支支吾吾什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is it you are not saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.14,0:41:25.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以撒 看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac... look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.31,0:41:32.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你们此次的真实经过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me the truth about your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.89,0:41:41.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,患者现在在大陆正南方向\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The injured is due South, inland,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.89,0:41:44.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,通往波士顿的一条树林路中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}on the wooded path to Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.80,0:41:47.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,驾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.97,0:41:49.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.97,0:43:35.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁在那 快现身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who's there? Show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.77,0:43:38.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.08,0:43:39.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我叫柏翠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The name is Petrus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.88,0:43:43.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不到一小时之前 我看到你睡着了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not an hour ago, I spied you sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.25,0:43:47.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看到你受伤了 我就回去给你拿了一些药\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and, seeing your grave wound, I have returned with medicinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.02,0:43:50.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,停 不要再靠近我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop. Not one step closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.29,0:43:53.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 先生 你已经感染了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But, sir, an infection has already taken root.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.26,0:43:56.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要担心 救助人员马上到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do not worry yourself. Aid is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.86,0:44:00.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是你不疼吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you are in pain, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.63,0:44:06.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我带了这个药可以减轻你的疼痛感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have concocted a simple physic to ease your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.40,0:44:12.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁都不该像你一样遭受这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No creature, man or animal, should suffer as you do, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.11,0:44:15.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.86,0:44:33.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你给我的是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What have you given me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.53,0:44:37.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am truly sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.64,0:44:43.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她创造了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.21,0:44:49.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们要把他带到你的小屋去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We will take him to your shack
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.25,0:44:50.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,直到危险解除\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}until the threat has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.65,0:44:53.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利 你就真的认为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did you really think it would be so easy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.35,0:44:56.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能如此简单的逃过我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to escape us, Mr. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.92,0:45:03.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这 向前走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There, up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.00,0:45:11.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治 乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}George? George?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.67,0:45:17.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是他的仆人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're the servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.37,0:45:19.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 是西布利夫人派来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, sir, sent by Mrs. Sibley
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.18,0:45:20.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,找回她生病的丈夫的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to retrieve her ailing husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.74,0:45:23.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这比我想象的还要糟糕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is worse than I had feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.18,0:45:25.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以我才要他立即去医院治疗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Which is why he needs to be taken to hospital at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.38,0:45:26.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.45,0:45:29.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,困扰我的不是他的病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is not the injury that troubles me,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.35,0:45:31.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而是他如何得病的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but how he came by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.52,0:45:34.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他试图摆脱女巫对他的控制\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He sought to free himself from the witches' grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.12,0:45:35.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不懂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.83,0:45:37.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他没生病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The man is not ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.70,0:45:41.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他被下咒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He has been spelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.70,0:45:44.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你对这知道多少\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Might you know something about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.94,0:45:52.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,黑尔小姐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Miss Hale.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.94,0:45:55.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你记不记得那天下午在墓园\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you remember that afternoon in the graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.01,0:45:56.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你向我暗示我的父亲并不是我们所想的那样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when you implied my father is not who he seems?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.95,0:45:58.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,记得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.95,0:46:02.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请我进来 我告诉你为什么我也这么觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Invite me inside, and I'll tell you why I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.50,0:46:23.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 西布利先生在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me... where is Mr. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.01,0:46:24.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们有麻烦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.44,0:46:25.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那不是我的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That was not my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.74,0:46:27.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要么知道他在哪 要么就不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Either you know where he is, or you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.78,0:46:29.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我确实知道他在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I do know where he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.15,0:46:30.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而那就是问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and that is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.71,0:46:33.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,牧师认为他被下咒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Reverend has deemed him a victim of witchcraft
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.32,0:46:36.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,决定带着乔治去他那边休养\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and has decided that George is to rest under his care.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.72,0:46:39.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们应该快一点了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Quickly now. Make haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.12,0:46:40.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.82,0:46:43.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柏翠的巫术只能维持一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Petrus' physic will last but a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.16,0:46:44.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在那\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There. There.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.83,0:46:48.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后 西布利会醒来 神志清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And then Mr. Sibley will awake, lucid and eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.23,0:46:51.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,会亟不可待地告诉因科瑞斯一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To tell Increase everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.10,0:46:53.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
